title: Houston Faith Church - Videos
description:
Houston Faith Church Channel is a true, New Testament, Bible-anchored, Spirit-filled resource that helps unbelievers meet God through Jesus Christ and builds strong Christians who can change their world. What you’ll find here is a wealth of spiritual insight into God's word, and how you can apply it to your own life. And you’ll also find that your hope is awakened, your faith rises, and your purpose in life becomes clear. 

God is good. He loves people. And His plan for your life is almost unbelievably wonderful! Just believe it!
